    "Each model was trained independently on the training set, without any modifications or pre-training specific to the task, to evaluate their out-of-thebox spam detection capabilities.",
    "The validation set was used iteratively during training to adjust parameters and prevent overfitting.",
    "Finally, the testing set provided a benchmark for comparing the final performance of both models, applying the defined evaluation metrics to assess and compare their effectiveness in accurately classifying spam and ham emails.",
    "The results of this study are presented in this section.",
    "Results of ChatGPT-4The evaluation of ChatGPT-4's performance in spam detection on the SpamAssassin public mail corpus reveals insightful outcomes."
